Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kenticocloud.delivery.Element
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssetsElement, DateTimeElement, ModularContentElement, MultipleChoiceElement, NumberElement, TaxonomyElement, TextElement, UrlSlugElement

    public abstract class Element
extends java.lang.Object
    Parent object model of individual elements

    When retrieving content items or content types, you get an elements collection as a part of the retrieved item or type.
